31#include "gmp.h"
32#include "gmp-impl.h"
33
34int
35mpf_init_set_str (mpf_ptr r, const char *s, int base)
36{
37 mp_size_t prec = __gmp_default_fp_limb_precision;
38 r->_mp_size = 0;
39 r->_mp_exp = 0;
40 r->_mp_prec = prec;
41 r->_mp_d = __GMP_ALLOCATE_FUNC_LIMBS (prec + 1);
42
43 return mpf_set_str (r, s, base);
44}
